 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Sap-sipper:

    Whenever a grass-type move 
  hits this Pokémon, its Attack 
  rises one stage, negating any 
  other effect on it.

  Hydration:

    This Pokémon is cured of any 
  major status ailment after each 
  turn during rain.

  Gooey:

    Lowers attacking Pokémon's 
  Speed by one stage on contact.


